就知佢on9仔買分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8a3b985c967fb0f6e7cb8e425a22f60f170866","tid":307141,"uid":63670,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"主要係個個翻工翻學嘆到嘔<br />\n有一隻同lol差唔多玩法（好玩）<br />\n節奏又夠快<br />\n排位模式<br />\n雖然畫質有待改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪個個都玩當消磨時間囉<br />\n都有一定關係係有女同方便（手機）<br />\n同帶上係d尿袋都越出越多"},{"pid":"ef072feefc73dbc06e347eabd632da60fb19eb42","tid":307141,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"手機game都要代打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6663ff58427ec7fc8ed4e29cb36cf29aa43b2c3","tid":307141,"uid":90643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"係大陸好多女玩王者，請代打上王者之後溝女都易啲"},{"pid":"d47ae1eb6897f9d414a57b2adcb0e3b6850f319b","tid":307141,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9aba55bc9e6e2522a1f924a6c0fb6307e5b0895","tid":307141,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ab5a4e37a77bd5dcc83af969a2b6537efaccba8","tid":307141,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係唔明手機game 有咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n玩過王者就明 真正輕鬆玩</blockquote><br />\n點輕鬆法？"},{"pid":"64060828b2774776e41b0c08c96523a762d4b4fa","tid":307141,"uid":283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:02:57.000Z","msg":"一打真係唔識停"},{"pid":"27bf709c67d2fa4d470853e8bb9cee9d57796dc7","tid":307141,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adf6480e064aa9ff1da6e7f640ca7c4ad9850a88","tid":307141,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:06:00.000Z","msg